26:29.321 --> 26:32.289
I'm so sorry.

26:32.291 --> 26:35.359
I'm so sorry, Norma.

26:37.964 --> 26:40.598
Please forgive me.

27:07.258 --> 27:10.194
- looking for something?

27:12.297 --> 27:14.398
- Maggie, come on, where is it?
Where'd you put it?

27:14.400 --> 27:16.233
- I'm not giving it
to you, Alex.

27:16.235 --> 27:17.835
Don't do something stupid

27:17.837 --> 27:17.835
and get yourself killed.

