27:35.221 --> 27:37.655
What happened?

27:37.657 --> 27:39.223
I know you.

27:39.225 --> 27:41.692
I know you live
by your own moral compass.

27:41.694 --> 27:45.295
I know there's
a reason you're here.

27:51.937 --> 27:54.238
something about Norma bates?

28:03.015 --> 28:06.417
did she kill herself?

28:06.419 --> 28:08.919
- No.

28:08.921 --> 28:10.688
- And you know who did kill her?

28:10.690 --> 28:13.157
Or you think you do?

28:16.128 --> 28:18.429
- I just--i need my damn gun,
so just make it show up

28:18.431 --> 28:20.698
by the time I'm strong enough
to leave here.

28:49.494 --> 28:51.995
- mother.

28:55.200 --> 28:57.968
What--why--how long
have you been here?

28:57.970 --> 29:01.205
- Only a little while, honey.

29:01.207 --> 29:05.275
Just wanted to check in
with you after everything.

29:06.746 --> 29:08.479
And we gotta talk about Dylan.

29:08.481 --> 29:11.381
- What about Dylan?

29:11.383 --> 29:12.950
- He can't be here.

29:12.952 --> 29:15.085
- What--he's not gonna stay.

29:15.087 --> 29:17.054
- Well, he's asking
a lot of questions,

29:17.056 --> 29:18.489
and you can't let him
know the answers.

29:18.491 --> 29:20.057
- I won't, mother.

29:20.059 --> 29:22.159
I would never do anything
to jeopardize us.

29:22.161 --> 29:24.061
- He's your brother.
I know you love him.

29:24.063 --> 29:25.395
But you can't let him in.

29:25.397 --> 29:27.030
- He's just visiting.

29:27.032 --> 29:28.365
- Norman, I'm sure
he's coming at it

29:28.367 --> 29:31.769
from a good place, but...

29:31.771 --> 29:33.504
Unfortunately,
he's just misguided.

29:33.506 --> 29:36.340
He's never really understood us.

29:36.342 --> 29:38.208
Don't get me wrong,
i love Dylan.

29:38.210 --> 29:41.411
We both love Dylan.
I mean, it's Dylan.

29:41.413 --> 29:43.213
But the reality is that we--

29:43.215 --> 29:45.482
we can't have him
in our lives anymore.

29:47.353 --> 29:51.388
That's the price we pay
for having what we have.

29:51.390 --> 29:54.992
It's just the two of us.

29:56.295 --> 29:58.128
- I understand, mother.

29:58.130 --> 30:00.497
'Kay.

30:04.570 --> 30:06.336
you just need to, like,

30:06.338 --> 30:09.106
cook a nice little dinner
for the two of you.

30:09.108 --> 30:11.108
You know, charm him.
Be happy.

30:11.110 --> 30:12.476
Convince him that you're fine.

30:12.478 --> 30:14.278
And then make him leave.

30:14.280 --> 30:16.280
- Okay.

30:16.282 --> 30:17.414
- Okay.

30:34.265 --> 30:35.432
- Dylan?

30:35.434 --> 30:36.600
- Yeah.

30:36.602 --> 30:38.068
Any luck?

30:38.070 --> 30:39.336
- We called
your brother's doctor

30:39.338 --> 30:41.338
to see if we could renew
the expired prescription,

30:41.340 --> 30:44.041
but unfortunately
we couldn't speak to him.

30:44.043 --> 30:47.277
Dr. Edwards went missing
just over a year ago.

30:47.279 --> 30:50.080
Apparently, he's presumed dead.

30:56.422 --> 30:58.322
- i--i guess my brother
was confused.

30:58.324 --> 31:01.225
You know, he--he said that
he saw him a few days ago,

31:01.227 --> 31:03.260
but that's why
he needs the meds.

31:06.532 --> 31:08.298
I'm--

31:08.300 --> 31:10.434
I'm worried that if he
doesn't get his meds soon,

31:10.436 --> 31:12.269
then something
very bad will happen.

31:32.590 --> 31:34.458
can I help you?

31:34.460 --> 31:35.492
- Hi.

31:35.494 --> 31:37.194
- Hi.
Who are you?

31:37.196 --> 31:39.263
- I'm Madeleine.
I'm a friend of Norman's.

31:39.265 --> 31:41.498
Who are you?

31:41.500 --> 31:44.368
- I'm--I'm--I'm Dylan.
I'm Norman's brother.

31:44.370 --> 31:47.371
- Oh.

31:47.373 --> 31:49.239
- You didn't know
that he had a brother.

31:49.241 --> 31:51.475
- No.

31:51.477 --> 31:52.542
Well, I'm just

31:52.544 --> 31:55.245
going in to see Norman.

31:55.247 --> 31:58.615
My husband's missing;
He never came home, and...

31:58.617 --> 32:00.584
I just really need
to talk to Norman.

32:00.586 --> 32:01.952
I think he might have seen him.

32:04.690 --> 32:06.590
- Your husband was here?

32:06.592 --> 32:07.958
- I don't know.

32:07.960 --> 32:09.660
I--he might have been.

32:09.662 --> 32:11.495
I just don't know
where else to go.

32:11.497 --> 32:12.462
I've been calling and--

32:12.464 --> 32:13.931
- look, I'm--I'm really sorry

32:13.933 --> 32:15.365
about your husband, okay?

32:15.367 --> 32:17.401
But Norman is in a really
fragile state right now,

32:17.403 --> 32:20.671
and i--i just--i don't--
i don't want him to get upset.

32:21.707 --> 32:23.273
Okay, so if--if you want,

32:23.275 --> 32:24.541
I can--i can tell him
that you called,

32:24.543 --> 32:26.977
and I'm sure he'll--
he'll call you back.

32:26.979 --> 32:28.278
- Wait, what--
what do you mean?

32:28.280 --> 32:29.513
What's wrong with Norman?

32:33.485 --> 32:36.186
- n-Norman has...

32:36.188 --> 32:37.955
Norman has mental issues.

32:37.957 --> 32:39.957
Okay, he--he's--he's not well.

32:39.959 --> 32:41.291
That's all I can really say.

32:41.293 --> 32:43.327
Look, i--i just--
i really need to

32:43.329 --> 32:44.995
try and get him
into a safe place

32:44.997 --> 32:47.631
and control his
environment, okay?

32:47.633 --> 32:49.967
- I'm so sorry, i--

32:49.969 --> 32:51.001
I had no idea.

32:52.538 --> 32:54.304
- look, why don't--
why don't you just give me

32:54.306 --> 32:55.739
your husband's name
and I can ask him myself

32:55.741 --> 32:59.009
if he's seen him and--
um, I'm sure he'll let you know.

32:59.011 --> 33:00.577
- Sam loomis.

33:00.579 --> 33:01.979
- Okay.

33:26.138 --> 33:27.137
- Norman?

33:30.275 --> 33:32.709
- yeah, I'm just, uh,
just in the kitchen, Dylan.

33:32.711 --> 33:34.211
Putting out dinner.

33:34.213 --> 33:36.213
Everything okay?

34:01.440 --> 34:04.141
- pretty much done.

34:06.445 --> 34:09.379
- what's wrong?

34:09.380 --> 34:10.781
- We need to talk.

34:10.783 --> 34:15.385
I just ran into
someone named Madeleine.

34:17.556 --> 34:19.755
- I see. You, uh,

34:19.757 --> 34:21.190
you did, huh?

34:22.194 --> 34:25.062
- she was looking for
her husband?

34:27.498 --> 34:30.199
- hm, yes, the--the loomises.

34:31.503 --> 34:33.270
I've spent some time
with them both.

34:33.272 --> 34:35.072
I mean,

34:35.074 --> 34:36.339
I don't know them that well.

34:36.341 --> 34:38.175
And I certainly don't know
where he is.

34:38.177 --> 34:39.842
W-why don't you just sit on down

34:39.844 --> 34:41.478
and--and then we can eat, okay?

34:54.560 --> 34:56.525
- mm.

35:05.104 --> 35:06.603
- do you know what
happened to him, Norman?

35:11.143 --> 35:12.175
- No.

35:12.177 --> 35:14.244
No, of course
i don't know, Dylan.

35:14.246 --> 35:16.113
Come on--can we just
talk about this after--

35:16.115 --> 35:18.882
- no, we cannot
talk about this after.

35:18.884 --> 35:21.418
Okay, we're gonna
talk about this right now.

35:22.588 --> 35:24.121
Madeleine said that
she thought that

35:24.123 --> 35:25.388
he might have
come here yesterday.

35:25.390 --> 35:26.857
Did he come here yesterday?

35:31.830 --> 35:34.498
- mm-hmm.
Yes, he did.

35:34.500 --> 35:38.368
Dylan, he--he happened
to be here yesterday.

35:38.370 --> 35:39.870
- And what happened?

35:39.872 --> 35:41.905
- Well, you--

35:41.907 --> 35:45.575
y-y-you--you see the problem is,
Dylan, is that

35:45.577 --> 35:50.213
he was...
Not a very nice man.

35:52.151 --> 35:53.483
and he came here because

35:53.485 --> 35:56.386
he was cheating on Madeleine
with this other woman,

35:56.388 --> 35:58.155
and she rented a room.

35:58.157 --> 36:00.824
You know, just--
just so they could, uh,

36:00.826 --> 36:03.627
you know, spend
a few hours together.

36:05.931 --> 36:07.497
- and then what happened?
- I don't know.

36:07.499 --> 36:09.866
In--in the morning,
they just weren't here.

36:09.868 --> 36:12.169
All right, they--
they must have just

36:12.171 --> 36:13.637
left together in
the middle of the night.

36:13.639 --> 36:16.173
I mean....

36:16.175 --> 36:17.574
Took the car, you know,

36:17.576 --> 36:19.209
it's the sort of thing
that happens, isn't it?

36:19.211 --> 36:20.510
It does make sense
that he would not

36:20.512 --> 36:22.445
be calling his wife today.

36:22.447 --> 36:24.281
- And--and you don't know
where they went?

36:24.283 --> 36:25.916
- No, no, of course
i don't know, Dylan.

36:25.918 --> 36:28.285
I don't know anything more
than what I've just told you.

36:28.287 --> 36:30.320
So please stop trying
to confuse me

36:30.322 --> 36:33.623
and you stop meddling with
the truth.

36:38.897 --> 36:40.630
okay, I know you care
about me, Dylan...

36:43.602 --> 36:45.335
but you can't ever understand.

36:45.337 --> 36:48.705
So please, please
just leave me be,

36:48.707 --> 36:51.942
and let me live
how I need to live.

36:51.944 --> 36:53.543
Okay, you can't
even be here, okay?

36:53.545 --> 36:57.347
So i--i think that you
really should leave soon.

37:21.306 --> 37:25.342
- I just really want
to help you get better.

37:25.344 --> 37:27.744
Okay, you need
to trust me, please?

37:38.389 --> 37:41.258
i-i got the pharmacy
to give me a few pills,

37:41.260 --> 37:43.293
until we can get you
a new prescription.

37:44.763 --> 37:47.464
we need to get you some help.

37:47.466 --> 37:50.700
And you need to start
taking these again.

37:50.702 --> 37:54.304
You were doing
really well on them.

37:55.974 --> 37:57.374
please just take one
in front of me

37:57.376 --> 37:59.743
so I know you're taking it.

38:50.462 --> 38:53.563
- Please stay out of this,
mother.

38:59.037 --> 39:02.005
I just want to
talk to him, Norman.

39:11.582 --> 39:13.550
Dylan.

39:19.423 --> 39:22.492
Dylan, I know you mean well.

39:27.798 --> 39:30.700
Because you have
always meant well.

39:33.037 --> 39:35.705
And you may not believe me,

39:35.707 --> 39:38.641
but I am so proud of you.

39:39.810 --> 39:42.679
I love you.

39:46.751 --> 39:48.518
But unfortunately,

39:48.520 --> 39:52.856
I can only ever be
a real mother to one person.

39:52.858 --> 39:56.092
And so even though

39:56.094 --> 39:59.796
I love you so very much,

39:59.798 --> 40:01.798
and this pains me...

40:05.102 --> 40:06.503
You're getting in the way.

40:09.808 --> 40:10.840
Mother! No!

40:13.678 --> 40:15.412
Not him!

40:15.414 --> 40:16.813
- Norman, let go!

40:17.816 --> 40:19.816
let go!

40:23.755 --> 40:24.788
Norman.

40:26.124 --> 40:28.825
Stop it, mother!

40:31.763 --> 40:33.463
- Get off!

40:33.465 --> 40:35.198
Mother!

41:01.460 --> 41:03.793
